      <title>菲律宾进行海上巡逻以检查中国科考船的存在</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-conducts-marine-patrols-check-presence-chinese-research-ships-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾周一部署一艘海岸警卫队船只在该国北部和东部海域执行为期两周的巡逻任务，以加强其海上存在，并对在宾汉隆起发现的中国科考船进行检查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-conducts-marine-patrols-check-presence-chinese-research-ships-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 02:05:22 GMT</pubDate>
