      <title>韩国和美国军队开始针对朝鲜威胁的年度演习</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-troops-kick-off-annual-drills-over-north-threats-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官员们表示，韩国和美国军队周一开始了春季演习，参加的部队人数是去年的两倍，因为这两个盟国寻求更好地应对朝鲜日益增加的核威胁和导弹威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-troops-kick-off-annual-drills-over-north-threats-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 02:01:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
